; Coverage for op.cc O_LOOKUP calc path and expression error context:
; Attempting to access a member on a null/void value triggers the
; scope lookup error path. This also exercises O_LOOKUP printing
; in the error context (op.cc lines 767-772).

2024/01/01 Test
    Expenses:Food    $100.00
    Assets:Cash

test reg --format "%(null.amount)\n" -> 1
__ERROR__
While calculating format expression:
  (null.amount)
While evaluating value expression:
  (null.amount)
While handling posting from "$FILE", line 7:
>     Expenses:Food    $100.00
Error: Expected return of a scope, but received an uninitialized value
end test
